&lt;li&gt;Develop and execute customized project plans for each client, ensuring a smooth and timely implementation process in line with SLAs while managing different external and internal stakeholders.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ensure new customers quickly realize the value of Payhawk by maximizing adoption during the initial implementation phase and aligning the setup with their business needs.&lt;/li&gt;
